| **Attack** | Incorporeal touch +3 melee touch (1d4 Wisdom drain) |
| **Full Attack** | Incorporeal touch +3 melee touch (1d4 Wisdom drain) |
| **Space/Reach** | 5 ft./5 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Babble, madness, Wisdom drain |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., incorporeal traits, +2 turn resistance, undead traits, undead resonance |
| **Saves** | Fort +1, Ref +2, Will +4 |
| **Abilities** | Str —, Dex 12, Con —, Int 11, Wis 11, Cha 18 |
| **Skills** | Hide +8, Intimidate +7, Listen +7, Search +7, Spot +7 |
| **Feats** | Improved Initiative, Lightning Reflexes |
| **Elemental Affinity** | Fragmented — distorted remnant of original Kin’s elemental identity |
| **Environment** | Kinsweave (border-kingdom ruins, abandoned guild halls, fallen court chambers); Tidebloom Reach (drowned villages near Hillmeet and Foxfen, waterlogged libraries). Rare in the Infinite Desert near collapsed Giant record-halls. |
