| **Speed** | 20 ft. (4 squares), fly 30 ft. (poor) |
| **Armor Class** | 17 (+1 size, +4 Dex, +2 natural), touch 15, flat-footed 13 |
| **Base Attack/Grapple** | +1/+0 |
| **Attack** | Slam +5 melee (1d4+4) |
| **Full Attack** | Slam +5 melee (1d4+4) |
| **Space/Reach** | 5 ft./5 ft. |
