| **Size/Type** | Small Elemental (Fire) |
| **Hit Dice** | 2d8+2 (11 hp) |
| **Initiative** | +0 |
| **Speed** | 30 ft. (6 squares) |
| **Armor Class** | 15 (+1 size, +0 Dex, +4 natural), touch 11, flat-footed 15 |
| **Base Attack/Grapple** | +1/–3 |
| **Attack** | Slam +2 melee (1d6 plus 1d6 fire plus combustion) |
| **Full Attack** | Slam +2 melee (1d6 plus 1d6 fire plus combustion) |
| **Space/Reach** | 5 ft./5 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Combustion, fiery aura |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., elemental traits, immunity to fire, vulnerability to cold, damage reduction 5/magic, melt weapons, elemental resonance (fire) |
| **Saves** | Fort +4, Ref +0, Will +0 |
