| **Space/Reach** | 10 ft./5 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Improved grab, pounce, rake 1d8+3, shadow step |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., low-light vision, scent, shadow form, damage reduction 5/magic, elemental resonance (shadow-earth) |
| **Saves** | Fort +11, Ref +11, Will +5 |
| **Abilities** | Str 23, Dex 18, Con 18, Int 5, Wis 14, Cha 10 |
| **Skills** | Hide +10 (+18 in dim light), Listen +8, Move Silently +14, Spot +8 |
