| **Challenge Rating** | 2 |
| **Treasure** | None (offerings — flowers, honey-water, silk ribbons, and small crafted gifts left at the bonded tree by halfling communities) |
| **Alignment** | Usually neutral good |
| **Advancement** | 5–8 HD (Medium) |
