| **Size/Type** | Large Magical Beast |
| **Hit Dice** | 4d10+12 (34 hp) |
| **Initiative** | +2 |
| **Speed** | 60 ft. (12 squares), fly 120 ft. (average) |
| **Armor Class** | 14 (–1 size, +2 Dex, +3 natural), touch 11, flat-footed 12 |
| **Base Attack/Grapple** | +4/+12 |
| **Attack** | Hoof +7 melee (1d6+4) |
| **Full Attack** | 2 hooves +7 melee (1d6+4) and bite +2 melee (1d3+2) |
| **Space/Reach** | 10 ft./5 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | — |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., low-light vision, scent, spell resistance 19, elemental resonance (air — pure) |
| **Saves** | Fort +7, Ref +6, Will +4 |
