| **Full Attack** | 2 slams +8 melee (1d6+5) or fat-knife +8 melee (1d4+5 plus fat-drain) and slam +6 melee (1d6+2) |
| **Space/Reach** | 5 ft./5 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Fat-drain, paralytic grasp, consume flesh |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., undead traits, damage reduction 5/silver, fast healing 3, cold immunity, scent, pass-trail, elemental resonance (earth — dead cold mountain) |
