| **Attack** | Claw +14 melee (1d6+4 plus terror-touch) |
| **Full Attack** | 2 claws +14 melee (1d6+4 plus terror-touch) and bite +12 melee (1d8+2) |
| **Space/Reach** | 5 ft./5 ft. |
