| **Initiative** | +1 |
| **Speed** | 20 ft. (4 squares) |
| **Armor Class** | 22 (–1 size, +1 Dex, +12 natural), touch 10, flat-footed 21 |
| **Base Attack/Grapple** | +15/+25 |
| **Attack** | +3 longspear +22 melee (2d6+9 plus 1d8 fire) or tail slap +20 melee (2d8+3 plus 1d8 fire) |
| **Full Attack** | +3 longspear +22/+17/+12 melee (2d6+9 plus 1d8 fire) and tail slap +18 melee (2d8+3 plus 1d8 fire) |
| **Space/Reach** | 10 ft./10 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Heat, constrict 2d8+3 plus 1d8 fire, improved grab, spell-like abilities |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., fire immunity, cold vulnerability, damage reduction 15/magic, spell resistance 22, elemental resonance (fire — sovereign forge) |
| **Saves** | Fort +12, Ref +10, Will +13 |
| **Abilities** | Str 22, Dex 13, Con 16, Int 18, Wis 18, Cha 19 |
