| **Initiative** | +3 |
| **Speed** | 30 ft. (6 squares), swim 40 ft. |
| **Armor Class** | 19 (+3 Dex, +6 natural), touch 13, flat-footed 16 |
| **Base Attack/Grapple** | +8/+11 |
| **Attack** | Claw +11 melee (1d6+3 plus dread-touch) |
| **Full Attack** | 2 claws +11 melee (1d6+3 plus dread-touch) and serpent bite +9 melee (1d4+1 plus poison) and vulture bite +9 melee (1d4+1) |
