| **Full Attack** | 2 claws +17 melee (2d6+6 plus 1d6 cold plus wendigo hunger) and bite +15 melee (1d8+3 plus 1d6 cold) |
| **Space/Reach** | 10 ft./10 ft. |
| **Special Attacks** | Wendigo hunger, howl, windwalk possession |
| **Special Qualities** | Darkvision 60 ft., damage reduction 10/cold iron and fire, spell resistance 22, cold immunity, fire vulnerability, regeneration 5 (fire), scent, elemental resonance (air — frozen wind, corrupted Brother) |
| **Saves** | Fort +13, Ref +14, Will +12 |
| **Abilities** | Str 22, Dex 22, Con 20, Int 14, Wis 18, Cha 18 |
