| **Feats** | Alertness, Dodge, Improved Initiative, Weapon Finesse |
| **Elemental Affinity** | Youngest Brother (Air) — deceptive; the resonance of air that misleads, the Youngest Brother’s domain at its most treacherous — not the honest wind of the steppe but the false light of the marsh, air that lies |
